# The pipeline needs NO database and NO API keys to build the dataset.
# The source of truth is the JSON files in pose-vocabularies/, and the two
# network-touching steps use public, unauthenticated endpoints:
#
#   - scripts/fetch-wikidata-positions.mjs  → Wikidata SPARQL (public, CC0)
#   - scripts/build-pose-dataset.mjs        → reads local files only
#
# The ONLY credential in the whole flow is a Hugging Face WRITE token, and it
# is used by the `hf` CLI for the final upload step, not by any script here:
#
#   pip install -U "huggingface_hub[cli]"
#   hf auth login          # paste a WRITE token scoped to the EthnicErotic org
#
# This file exists to document that there is nothing to configure. Copy it to
# .env if your tooling expects one; leaving it empty is fine.
